title: Analysis of Field Materials
description: A seminar for students who have completed a full-time field study. Devoted to the systematic analysis of field materials, integrating appropriate concepts and relevant literature, as well as utilizing the experience of other students.

pre_req_data.text: Prerequisite(s): satisfaction of the Entry Level Writing and Composition requirements, CMMU 105A, CMMU 105B, and CMMU 105C. Enrollment is restricted to community studies majors.
